SELECT *
FROM employees
WHERE id IN (
  SELECT employee_id
  FROM compensation
  WHERE employee_id IN (
    SELECT id
    FROM employees
    WHERE department_id IN (
      SELECT id FROM departments
    )
  )
)
AND status = 'active';

optimize this query

SELECT 
  e.id,
  e.name,
  d.name AS department_name,
  (
    SELECT SUM(c.amount)
    FROM compensation c
    WHERE c.employee_id = e.id
  ) AS total_compensation
FROM employees e
LEFT JOIN departments d ON e.department_id = d.id
WHERE e.status = 'active'
AND e.id IN (
  SELECT employee_id
  FROM compensation
  WHERE year >= 2022
);
